---
title: Sweet Thai Chili Burgers with Ginger Scallion Aioli, Crispy Onions & Sweet Potato Wedges
description: Our chefs believe creating the perfect patty is like writing a hit song: Pack it with the right ingredients and it sings. Tonight’s patties open with ground beef, then build to a stunning chorus thanks to ginger, garlic, and soy sauce. And if you’re looking for that key change, we’ve got the sauce for you—a creamy ginger scallion aioli, sweet Thai chili sauce and crispy fried onions. This meal wouldn't be complete without a side of sweet potato wedges to dip into any extra aioli. Now that’s a Top 40 burger!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/sweet-thai-chili-burgers-674e40bb.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.com/recipecards/card/sweet-thai-chili-burgers-636130d40926e129b30f184b-415d516d.pdf
time required: 35 minutes
